    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can just cast it, adding suppress warnings if you like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>@SuppressWarnings(\"unchecked\")    \nAsyncCallback&lt;ResponseX&gt; callback = Mockito.any(AsyncCallback.class)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If Java allowed 'generic' generics they could have a method like this which is what you are looking for</p>\n\n<pre><code>private static &lt;T, E&gt; T&lt;E&gt; mock(Class&lt;T&lt;E&gt;&gt; clazz)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
