    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had to adopt the following mechamism to allow for generics:</p>\n\n<pre><code>import static org.mockito.Matchers.any;\nList&lt;String&gt; list = any();\nwhen(callMyMethod.getResult(list)).thenReturn(myResultString);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Hope this helps someone.</p>\n"
