      "body" : "I&#39;m wondering about a situation where the argument type is generic as well, but you only want to mock it for one concrete type (or mock it for multiple types in different ways). Given <code>when(x.y(any())).thenAnswer(...)</code> for example, where <code>y</code> is <code>public &lt;T&gt; T y(AsyncCallback&lt;T&gt; arg)</code>.  Perhaps it would be better to check the type in the answer, if that is what&#39;s needed?"
