    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Posting pierrefevrier comment as answer which might be useful if it present in a answer instead of comments.</p>\n\n<p>With new versions of Mockito: <code>(Matchers.&lt;AsyncCallback&lt;ResponseX&gt;&gt;any()</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 114996,
