  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7917635/mockito-any-pass-interface-with-generics",
  "title" : "Mockito.any() pass Interface with Generics",
  "body" : "<p>is it possible to pass the type of an interface with generics?</p>\n\n<p>The interface:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public interface AsyncCallback&lt;T&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In my test method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Mockito.any(AsyncCallback.class)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Putting <code>&lt;ResponseX&gt;</code> behind or for <code>.class</code> didnt work.</p>\n"
